snippet.title: Holo X Break reveal trailer (from the creators of HoloCure)
snippet.description:
Team HoloCure just revealed a new side-scrolling beat-em-up game called Holo X Break (with a silent X). A full trailer will be revealed after the HoloFes this month. 

Steam Page is now up 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2719150/Holo_X_Break/

This channel is NOT affiliated with Kay Yu, Team HoloCure, Cover Corp, or Hololive.
